text: José Antonio López Gil (born 11 July 1976 in San Pedro de Alcántara) is a Spanish former road racing cyclist. ==Palmarès== ;2002 :1st Clásica Ciudad de Torredonjimeno ;2003 :1st stage 7 Vuelta a Cuba ;2004 :2nd Memorial Manuel Galera ;2008 :1st stage 1 Vuelta a Andalucía ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male cyclists
